{"tid":408830,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"其實月餅憑咩賣咁貴？","createTime":"2017-09-21T14:06:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-21T15:11:09.000Z","uid":37501,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"01af43371ea862d6030541f088ad958bfa34b42c","tid":408830,"uid":37501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T14:06:51.000Z","msg":"明明係下欄野 ，料又唔係靚（睇過d爆料po就知製作過程幾唔衛生）<br />\n加上唔係好食，年年屋企有人送月餅卷全家只係食到一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其他就食剩就老豆有時扲黎做早餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n4個成本勁低但係賣差唔多4舊水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n癲撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c5c6f78d6ccc01ed995f0eb471154f845d134dc","tid":408830,"uid":24282,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T14:07:11.000Z","msg":"憑傲氣"},{"pid":"c689030600296340ba34c3ce109c7887ebaa3a7c","tid":408830,"uid":71725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T14:09:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e5f50ca0c885c9f75acb2b2e23a03c7bd943c425","tid":408830,"uid":9286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T14:11:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>4舊水，ching食乜月餅？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n聽該講半島月餅好貴 唔知係咪樓主講緊呢隻"},{"pid":"cbae9f9aed6f97d32b5c431a3f7f752488e67903","tid":408830,"uid":37501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T14:12:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>4舊水，ching食乜月餅？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n聽該講半島月餅好貴 唔知係咪樓主講緊呢隻</blockquote><br />\n我開po前上網check過價錢<br />\n美心雙黃白蓮蓉係35x喎<br />\n唔通個網資料有錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bc77f9969bfd5e5ef88e439fe0